action_description: This Action will toggle a Wemo Outdoor Plug on or off.
This Action will turn a Wemo Outdoor Plug off then immediately back on.
This Action will turn a Wemo Outdoor Plug on then immediately back off.
This Action will turn a Wemo Outdoor Plug off. If the Wemo Outdoor Plug is already off, it will remain off.
This Action will turn a Wemo Outdoor Plug on. If the Wemo Outdoor Plug is already on, it will remain on.
